- Completed OpenClaw internals research design. Key finding: before_prompt_build plugin hook is the main leverage point for automating pipeline context injection into agent sessions. Two hook layers: internal (event scripts) and plugin (lifecycle). 5 opportunities identified: pipeline-context injection [HIGH], agent turn logging [MEDIUM], native orchestrator tool [HIGH], bootstrap file hook [MEDIUM], auto-reply commands [LOW]. Plugins run in-process with no sandbox. instance:architect pipeline:research-openclaw-internals stage:architect_design *(memory/entries/2026-03-21_033036_completed-openclaw-internals-research-de.md)*
