- Equilibrium SNN build complete. Key lessons: (1) nbformat raw strings mangle quotes, use regular strings. (2) Ablations: zero DATA not model dimensions. (3) LambdaLR: base_lr * lambda, so set base_lr=lr_min. (4) TX costs on position changes only via np.diff. (5) Store raw probs for abstention. (6) LSTM baseline must match SNN TBPTT protocol exactly. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_154243_equilibrium-snn-build-complete-key-lesso.md)*
- Validate Scheme B build complete. Key decisions: (1) Exact V3 architecture frozen — SNNFinanceV3 with n_output=1 for regression, HuberLoss(delta=0.01), membrane readout from mem2. (2) 10 folds with deterministic boundaries: val_size = n_samples // (n_folds+1). (3) Block bootstrap with block_size=50 supplements IID bootstrap for non-independence. (4) DSR uses n_trials=10 (honest V3 search count). (5) Power analysis shows min detectable Sharpe depends on per-fold variance. (6) Wilcoxon signed-rank for paired control comparisons. (7) Abstention uses |predicted_delta| not probability — Scheme B outputs continuous regression value, not classification. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_154907_validate-scheme-b-build-complete-key-dec.md)*
- build-equilibrium-snn: Applied 2 fixes from Critic code review (APPROVED). FIX-1: Added 'import json' to Cell 5 imports — was missing, first used in Cell 6 json.dumps(). FIX-2: McNemar ABL-03 alignment — ABL-03 evaluate_fold_with_reset() includes all candles but EQ-04 evaluate_fold() excludes warmup candles. Fixed both Cell 50 (critical control test) and Cell 62 (Bonferroni McNemar loop) to trim warmup candles from ABL-03 raw_probs. Pattern: any comparison between persistent-state models (warmup excluded) and reset-per-candle models (all candles) needs alignment. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_155016_build-equilibrium-snn-applied-2-fixes-fr.md)*
- Session complete: 3 notebooks built + 1 critic fix. (1) build-equilibrium-snn: 65 cells, 21 experiments, TBPTT K=8, dual tonic+phasic, membrane readout. Critic fix: json import order, deterministic seeds via hashlib.md5, block bootstrap added. (2) validate-scheme-b: 51 cells, 12 experiments, frozen V3 Scheme B, 10 folds, DSR+bootstrap+sign test+Wilcoxon. (3) stack-specialists: 46 cells, 12 experiments, 3 SNN specialists retrained from V3, LR/RF stacking, anti-leakage Fold 3 hold-out. Key pattern: use nbformat builder scripts, avoid raw strings (quote mangling), zero DATA not model dims for ablations. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_171256_session-complete-3-notebooks-built-1-cri.md)*
