- Established superseded primitive lifecycle pattern. When primitives are replaced: add status:superseded + superseded_by field to old, supersedes field to new. embed_primitives.py filters both superseded and archived from boot indexes (AGENTS.md + MEMORY.md). Files stay in place for memory_search discovery. First use: tiny-snn-gpu-parallelism superseded by gpu-parallel-thrashing-t4. Decision primitive: decisions/superseded-primitive-lifecycle.md primitives conventions infrastructure *(memory/entries/2026-03-19_044734_established-superseded-primitive-lifecyc.md)*
- Local CPU experiment runner works. run_local.py in machinelearning/snn_applied_finance/scripts/ runs all 81 equilibrium experiments on the 4-core ARM server without GPU. Full run: ~2.5 hours with --workers 1. Models small enough (nano-15 to medium-192) that GPU adds no real advantage. Dead neuron re-initialization added to SNNEquilibriumV2: Kaiming reinit for <1% spike rate neurons every 5 epochs after warmup, preserves sparsity masks. torch.nn.Buffer requires .fill_() not direct float assignment. Results save to notebooks/local_results/ with incremental saves and --resume support. Saves Colab Pro hours for tasks that don't need GPU. infrastructure experiments cpu local-runner *(memory/entries/2026-03-19_133712_local-cpu-experiment-runner-works-run-lo.md)*
