- research-openclaw-internals analysis review: APPROVED 0 blocks 4 flags (1 med, 3 low). All 7/7 infra experiments verified against results_summary.json. FLAG-1 (LOW): injection payload growth extrapolation oversimplified. FLAG-2 (MED): accuracy-Sharpe decorrelation hypothesis untested — BL-06/BL-07 Sharpe outliers (-16 to -20) may be position sizing artifact, not SNN insight. Script 4 needs position sizing decomposition. FLAG-3 (LOW): scale-performance 'flat' claim overconfident for n=2-4 per scale. FLAG-4 (LOW): no hook catalog staleness checker. KEY INSIGHT: Infrastructure research analysis needs different review criteria than SNN pipelines — verify claims against structured data (JSON), not statistical tests. The auto-generated SNN template was correctly identified as test execution side-effect. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-critic/memory/entries/2026-03-21_044214_research-openclaw-internals-analysis-rev.md)*
- research-openclaw-internals analysis review: APPROVED 0 blocks 4 flags. KEY: (1) Always check training dynamics plots for anomalies — EQ-06/f0 near-zero loss invisible in tables but obvious in plot. (2) Even secondary SNN results need statistical caveats — 3-fold t-test p=0.04 with no multiple testing correction is exactly what slips through when framed as secondary. (3) Accuracy-Sharpe discrepancy (accurate on small moves, wrong on big moves) is testable hypothesis connecting to Scheme B. (4) Infrastructure pipelines need different review criteria than SNN pipelines — focus on verification methodology and recommendation prioritization. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-critic/memory/entries/2026-03-21_044611_research-openclaw-internals-analysis-rev.md)*
- Equilibrium SNN build complete. Key lessons: (1) nbformat raw strings mangle quotes, use regular strings. (2) Ablations: zero DATA not model dimensions. (3) LambdaLR: base_lr * lambda, so set base_lr=lr_min. (4) TX costs on position changes only via np.diff. (5) Store raw probs for abstention. (6) LSTM baseline must match SNN TBPTT protocol exactly. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_154243_equilibrium-snn-build-complete-key-lesso.md)*
- Validate Scheme B build complete. Key decisions: (1) Exact V3 architecture frozen — SNNFinanceV3 with n_output=1 for regression, HuberLoss(delta=0.01), membrane readout from mem2. (2) 10 folds with deterministic boundaries: val_size = n_samples // (n_folds+1). (3) Block bootstrap with block_size=50 supplements IID bootstrap for non-independence. (4) DSR uses n_trials=10 (honest V3 search count). (5) Power analysis shows min detectable Sharpe depends on per-fold variance. (6) Wilcoxon signed-rank for paired control comparisons. (7) Abstention uses |predicted_delta| not probability — Scheme B outputs continuous regression value, not classification. *(/home/ubuntu/.openclaw/workspace-builder/memory/entries/2026-03-18_154907_validate-scheme-b-build-complete-key-dec.md)*
