## 2026-03-19T20:45:09Z — decision ⚡⚡⚡⚡

Versioning clarification from Shael: The three concurrent pipelines (build-equilibrium-snn, stack-specialists, validate-scheme-b) are V5 Phase 1 — three parallel iterations exploring different architectural directions. The convergence proposal combining phasic-dominant equilibrium + Scheme B is V6 Phase 1 (new autonomous build), not a Phase 3 iteration. Proposal updated to phase1_proposal, pending_review.

