  ## 5.3 Phase 1 Nano-15 Experiments      (G2-01..06 — rate, delta, equilibrium × spike/continuous)
  ## 5.4 Phase 1 Nano-9 Experiments       (G3-01..06 — rate, delta, equilibrium × spike/continuous)
