# SNN Applied Finance

Apply SNN research to financial market prediction. Multi-agent trio design (architect → critic → builder).

## Current State
- V1: Collapsed to majority-class (50.61%), bear market artifact
- V2: 54.02% best accuracy, signal real but unprofitable after costs (4h BTC)
- V3: Scheme B +0.45 Sharpe via abstention (not significant), 3/5 specialist micro-networks work
- Quant baseline: logistic regression / random forest comparison complete

## Next Priority
- [[equilibrium-snn]] — continuous spike streaming architecture
- Specialist stacking (CrashDet + RallyDet + VolSpikeDet → logistic combiner)
- Longer timeframes (daily resolution, breakeven ~55.1%)

## Long-Term
- Paper trading → micro-live ($50-100/trade) → self-sustaining AI infrastructure
