# SNN Standard Model Benchmarks

Systematic benchmarking of snnTorch neuron models (Leaky, Synaptic, Alpha) on MNIST-family datasets. Foundation for custom Rhythm Neuron (Part II).

## Outcome
- Phase 1 (Leaky): 49 experiments, best β=0.99 steps=25 (96.10%)
- Phase 2 (Synaptic): 22 experiments complete
- Phase 3 (Alpha + cross-model + Fashion-MNIST): all 26 finished, 0 failures
- Full report: `reports/SNN_Progress_Report.md`